::BEGIN:MAIN
# Bless

Usage: cast 'bless' <victim | object>
Accum: No
Duration: 6 Hours, permanent for objects.
Level:  level 5.

p:Bless on a victim will improve the victims saving throw versus spells by 1, and furthermore improve the hitroll by 2.

p:Bless on an item currently has no defined action.  It is only possible to bless non-evil items, and the object blessed may weigh no more than five pounds per level of caster.
::END:MAIN
